## Import users

You can download an XLSX template, add users to the template by referencing
the sample's format, and then import the configured XLSX file to add the users
to the system.

Note that this feature does not support importing Microsoft 365 Groups.

Follow the steps blew to edit the user information in template and then import
users:

1\. Open the file in Excel and complete the information. For reference, go to
the Sample data sheet.

2\. Click Import and browse the XLSX file that you configured. Click Open. You
will see a message on the upper-right of the page after the import completes.
